## Practices

| Do | Don't |
| --- | --- |
| Backoff retries | Infinite retries |
| Explicit timeouts | Unbounded waits |
| Log external calls | Silent failures |
| Cache responses | Repeated identical calls |
| Secrets in secure storage | Hardcoded keys |

## Security Checklist

Required:

- [ ] Credentials from env vars or a secrets manager
- [ ] HTTPS only
- [ ] TLS certificate validation on

Forbidden:

- [ ] Logging API keys or tokens
- [ ] Ignoring or disabling certificate errors

